cs.RO, cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.PL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with multi-robot path planning and synchronization. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is also likely as the paper considers a team of robots working together to achieve a common goal. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper uses Linear Temporal Logic (LTL) to specify the mission and optimizing proposition. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper considers the non-deterministic traveling times of the robots and relies on communication capabilities to maintain performance. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is less likely but still possible as the paper proposes a method for computing optimal paths and synchronization sequences for the robots.
